Peru to Tax Currency Forwards Maturing Within 60 Days

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-11-29T22:13:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/peru-to-tax-currency-forwards-maturing-within-60-days-correct-.html
Peruvian sol forwards contracts
between local and offshore counterparties are now taxable if
they mature within 60 days, according to a decree published
today in the state gazette.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Quigley in Lima at 
 jquigley8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  